{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"content":["Place bacon into mixing bowl, place simmering basket instead of measuring cup onto mixing bowl lid and cook <strong>20 min\/250°F\/speed<\/strong> . Transfer bacon into a large bowl lined with paper towels. Allow to drain before removing paper towels and set aside.","Place garlic, mustard, olive oil, lemon juice, vinegar, salt and white pepper into mixing bowl and mix <strong><nobr>10 sec\/speed 8<\/nobr><\/strong>. Transfer to bowl with reserved bacon, combine with spatula and set aside.","Place water into mixing bowl. Place Varoma into position, weigh in potatoes and eggs, secure Varoma lid and steam <strong><nobr>27 min\/Varoma\/speed 3<\/nobr><\/strong>. Remove eggs from Varoma, immediately transfer to simmering basket and run under cold water to stop cooking process.","Peel eggs, transfer to a bowl and set aside. Stir potatoes with spatula to ensure even cooking, secure Varoma lid and steam a further <strong><nobr>10-15 min\/Varoma\/speed 3<\/nobr><\/strong>, or just until potatoes are cooked through.","Immediately transfer potatoes into bowl with bacon mixture, toss to coat potatoes and allow to cool (approx. 30 min.).","Place a bowl onto mixing bowl lid and weigh in celery, pickles, green onions, capers and mayonnaise. Transfer to bowl with potatoes and bacon mixture and combine well with spatula.","Slice eggs and arrange on top of potato salad. Serve chilled or at room temperature."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"","content":["8 oz bacon, cut into ½ in. pieces","2 garlic cloves","½ oz Dijon mustard","1 oz extra virgin olive oil","1 oz freshly squeezed lemon juice","1 oz white vinegar","1 tsp salt","¼ tsp ground white pepper","25 oz water","60 oz Yukon gold potatoes, peeled and cut into ½ in. pieces","4 large eggs","6 oz celery, cut into ¼ in. pieces","5 oz pickles, cut into ¼ in. pieces","3 oz green onions, cut into ¼ in. pieces (approx. 4 onions)","2 tbsp capers","2 oz mayonnaise"]}],"id":"r213375","imageLink":"https:\/\/4.bp.blogspot.com\/-1DSBy65cumk\/XZWZYh1J2zI\/AAAAAAAAeMI\/4OmiCvKerB4e4Rfe6gCnt2pHWNkQBf7nwCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_aQ-twA02lMlExJDZ.png","title":"Lemon Caper Potato Salad","publishedAt":"2017-06-23T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"8 g","fat":"17 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"30 g","calories":"1251 kJ \/ 299 kcal"},"usefulItems":"large bowl, paper towels","hintsAndTricks":["Add 1 oz more mayonnaise for a really creamy salad.","Cooling hot potatoes slightly before mixing with mayonnaise will prevent breaking the emulsion."],"basicInfo":["easy","20m","1h","12 portions"]}